#. Tag: screen
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:130
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The output can be a bit daunting, since one small mistake can cause a "
#| "cascade of errors. \n"
#| "The trick is to look at the first error, fix that error, save the file, "
#| "and run <command>meinproc5</command> again."
msgid ""
"The output can be a bit daunting, since one small mistake can cause a "
"cascade of errors. \n"
"The trick is to look at the first error, fix that error, save the file, and "
"run <command>meinproc6</command> again."
msgstr ""
"La sortie risque d'être un peu décourageante, car une seule petite faute est "
"capable de causer une cascade d'erreurs.\n"
"L'astuce consiste à examiner la première erreur, la corriger, enregistrer le "
"fichier et exécuter <command>meinproc5</command> à nouveau."

